snippet.title: Adventures of a Cat in Space - demo gameplay
snippet.description:
A selection of gameplay footage from the demo of Adventures of a Cat in Space showing the hand-drawn animation, some of the original music and the voice over from Doctor Who's Arthur Darvill.
-------------------------------
Official website: https://catinspace.co.uk/
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3265960/Adventures_of_a_Cat_in_Space/
Blue Sky: https://bsky.app/profile/catinspacegame.bsky.social
